column3: manufactureDescription

Featuring only premium steak with a robust flavor that’s rooted in sweet & savory seasoning, brown sugar and layers of hardwood smoke, Cattleman’s Cut Original Jerky is slow-cooked to deliver big, bold taste with every bite

When you start with slow-cooked premium steak, brown sugar, sweet and savory seasoning and layers of hardwood smoke, there isn’t much you can do to improve upon your delicious jerky. In fact, the only thing we could think of adding, is spicy fresh cracked black pepper.

By drenching our premium steak in a mixture of soy sauce, garlic, brown sugar and other savory seasonings and slow-cooking it for hours, we’ve created a timeless smoky-sweet teriyaki flavor that will leave you craving more.

FLANK STEAK JERKY There’s truly nothing on earth like our thick cuts of tender flank steak. These strips of premium meat are perfectly marinated in garlic, pepper and brown sugar to provide a sweet, rich start with a peppery kick. Make no mistake though, delicious beef is the flavor you’ll remember most.

REAL STEAK JERKY ORIGINAL RECIPE Some steaks come on a plate. Ours comes in a bag. Premium cuts of hand-picked beef are marinated in our Chef’s own soy sauce, horseradish and Worcestershire sauce. This unique blend, combined with our proprietary smoking process, gives our Original Recipe Real Steak Jerky the perfect proportion of salty, spicy and sweet.

REAL STEAK JERKY CHIPOTLE CRACKED PEPPER We combined the infamous chipotle chili, roasted jalapenos, and fresh cracked black pepper, to create an extra mouth-watering oomph to every bite. Yes, it’s hot. But trust us, it’s eat-the-entire-bag good.

REAL STEAK JERKY SWEET & SPICY Turns out, you can have it all in one bite. With a unique combination of a balanced sweetness followed by a pleasant kick of cayenne red pepper, Chef’s Cut Real Jerky Co Sweet and Spicy Steak Jerky is more flavor than you knew could fit in a bag

REAL STEAK JERKY ASIAN STYLE TERIYAKI We’ve packed a bag for you. Pairing premium steak with a zesty fusion of fresh pineapple, ginger, and green tea extract, Chef’s Cut Real Jerky Co Asian Style makes for an enticing twist on teriyaki that brings you flavors from far-away – no matter how far you go.

MANDARIN ORANGE TERIYAKI In my formative years, back in Kyoto, I was a world-renowned hibachi chef par excellence—differentiating myself from all the rest by using an orange as my secret weapon. Yep, I was the chef in the white apron and tall paper hat, slicing and dicing meats at lightning speeds, all while balancing a Samurai sword on the tip of my tongue—blindfolded. And trust me when I tell you, no one sets an onion volcano up in flames like I do. I’m a master.  Get out there. Be excellent.

ORIGINAL Yep, you guessed it. I’m the OG round here. The first flavor. The leader of the pack. Numero uno in this lineup. The original one. I go way back—like 2010 back. Since I’m hickory smoke with a black pepper and brown sugar marinade—I’ll always be delicious, no matter what. I’m what you call an instant classic. If I had an astrological sign, I’d be the star of this show. They’ve kept me around front and center all these years for one simple reason—because you never mess with perfection.  Get out there. Be original.

SWEET & SPICY BARBEQUE I know one thing about being sweet, and tad spicy—everything. What can I say? I’m a dual personality. It’s just who I am, who I’ve always been. From the very beginning. I’m just sweet from natural honey with an aged cayenne finish. But, don’t get it twisted. Even though my sweet side outweighs my spicy side, I’m still bold and even quite beefy. Tender, sweet, and totally savory—that’s me, Honey Spice.  Get Out There. Be bold.

Chili Lime Beef Right when you open the package, the delicious aroma of fresh lime will hit you. Then you’ll taste the bright spice of our hand-selected chilies. The perfect balance of flavor and spice, our Chili Lime Beef Jerky gives you just enough heat to get your mouth watering and the perfect accent of citrus to calm things down. It’s where sweet meets spicy — and you meet your new favorite snack.

Kung Pao Beef Chances are, you’ve had Kung Pao in one shape or form…but never like this! With our Kung Pao beef jerky, we don’t just dust the seasoning on top like other guys. The chilies, dark vinegar, brown sugar and Sichuan pepper are a part of our kettle cooking process, so it’s infused into every piece of beef. We do the work so you get all the spicy goodness of an expertly hand-crafted dish in every single tender bite.

Hickory Smoked Hearty foods have been said to put hair on your chest. Since the beginning of time, humans have relied on hearty foods to power thru....and grow hair. Look at Sasquatch. We cannot guarantee the hair growth, but we can guarantee that our Hickory Smoked Beef Jerky, slow cooked and smoked over hickory wood, will deliver a sweet, savory flavor that's delicious.

ORIGINAL BEEF JERKY From ancient migrations to modern snacking, meat has helped fuel humankind. We (arguably) didn't invent the awesome meat snack that is beef jerky — we just created the timeless flavor that put it on the map. Based on the Link family signature recipe, our Original Beef Jerky is slowly cooked over a special blend of hardwoods for the classic flavor America loves.

PEPPERED BEEF JERKY Sucky days and epic battles have always been a thing. Ask the Mongol Warriors. We did. They ate meat to power thru and pick it up a notch. When your day requires an extra kick, spice up your snack routine with Jack Link's Peppered Beef Jerky.

SRIRACHA BEEF JERKY They put that sh on everything and people love it! Great things happen when you marinate our premium, lean cuts of 100% beef with the sweet chili spice of Sriracha. It's a match made in mouth heaven.

STEAKHOUSE BEEF JERKY Forget white table cloths at snack time! Steakhouse Beef Jerky is calling BS on arrogant waiters that try to up-sell your steak. It's time to go back to basics with premium 100% beef and real ingredients that deliver great taste without a fuss.

SWEET & HOT BEEF JERKY What we have here is the best of both worlds. Heat and sweet. Lean cuts of 100% premium beef are marinated with a special blend of smoky sweet red chili and black pepper which build for an unforgettable chili heat perfectly balanced with a touch of sweet. Sweet & Hot Beef Jerky. We'd marry it.

TERIYAKI BEEF JERKY Beef jerky is synonymous with adventure. From Vikings crossing the seas to camping trips in the mountains, beef jerky is a portable fuel that can help power any journey. Our Teriyaki Beef Jerky is a flavor adventure you don't want to miss.

ORIGINAL BEEF JERKY Our gluten-free Original flavored beef jerky is lean and is made from Certified Organic beef raised by the humane standards required by the National Organic Program and NEVER given added hormones or antibiotics.

PEPPERED BEEF JERKY Our gluten-free Peppered flavored beef jerky is lean and is made from Certified Organic beef raised by the humane standards required by the National Organic Program and NEVER given added hormones or antibiotics.

TERIYAKI BEEF JERKY Our gluten-free Teriyaki flavored beef jerky is lean and is made from Certified Organic beef raised by the humane standards required by the National Organic Program and NEVER given added hormones or antibiotics.
Korean Recipe Barbecue Seasoned Beef Steak Strips Tender 100% grass-fed beef steak strips marinated in soy sauce, brown sugar, garlic and onion, then flame-kissed for char-grilled flavor.
Original Beef Steak Strips Tender 100% grass-fed beef steak strips seasoned in a simple blend of savory spices, then naturally smoked for a subtle, sweet finish.
Szechuan Peppercorn Beef Steak Strips Tender 100% grass-fed beef steak strips are seasoned with black and Szechuan peppercorns, then slow-smoked for a bold yet sweet flavor.

TRADITIONAL STYLE JERKY - HOT & SPICY You like a little heat in your life. We get it. That's why we make Old Trapper Hot & Spicy Beef Jerky. We season our already delicious jerky with spicy red pepper flakes and suddenly, that familiar savory-sweet flavor kicks you in the rear. This snack is great paired with a tall glass of your favorite beverage, ICE-COLD.

TRADITIONAL STYLE JERKY - OLD FASHIONED The Old Trapper legend began with our original Old Fashioned Beef Jerky. We season lean cuts of real steak, add brown sugar for just the right hint of sweetness, and smoke them to perfection using real wood in our smokehouses. The result is tender, never tough jerky that will be the best you’ve ever tasted.

TRADITIONAL STYLE JERKY - PEPPERED When you go to restaurants, are you embarrassed by how long you make the waiter grind fresh pepper onto your meal? If so, Old Trapper Peppered Jerky is your flavor. It’s seasoned with our own quality mix of spices and generous amounts of fresh black pepper, then smoked with real wood in our smokehouses until each piece is tender and juicy. But be warned, when you bite into Old Trapper Peppered jerky, it might bite you back.

TRADITIONAL STYLE JERKY - TERIYAKI To create the unique salty-sweet flavor in our Teriyaki beef jerky, we marinate lean beef strips in soy sauce and apple cider vinegar, season the cuts with our own mix of spices, then smoke them with real wood until they’re tender, juicy, and delicious. You deserve the best, eat Old Trapper.

Filet Mignon Chipotle Adobo Jerky Sweet & Tangy A fusion of east and west, our Chipotle Adobo flavor unites a traditional Filipino style marinade with our Mexican inspired Chipotle glaze. Sweet, pungent adobo seasoning blends with smoky, peppery Chipotle spices, creating a piquant balance. Our tender filets are marinated to magnificence and glazed to glory, offering a truly one of a kind jerky. We may be jerks, but this worldly jerky is spirited, yet refined.

Filet Mignon Memphis BBQ Jerky Spicy & Savory Superlative BBQ made unique for jerky. Using a quintessentially Memphis style blend of natural spices, we created a dry rub that starts off sweet. But beware, just when the seasoning happily layers your taste buds, the cayenne kicks you in the back of the mouth! With sweet heat, the meat is rubbed by hand with an array of seasonings, transporting you to the south. Treat yo self! We may be jerks, but this southern gentleman jerky is a little fiery, yet refined.

Filet Mignon Original Jerky Beefy & Savory Often imitated but never copied. Our traditional old school flavor brings you back to your granddaddy's jerky - salty, sweet and tangy with just the right amount of black pepper reminding you of the first time you tried beef jerky. But that memory turns on its head when you realize you have just met the new standard for deliciousness. Our tender filets are marinated to perfection, bringing you soft and iconic jerky. We may be jerks, but this traditional jerky is refined.

Filet Mignon Veri Veri Teriyaki Jerky Gingery & Garlicky Inspired by the flavors of Asian sauces and marinades, our Veri Veri Teriyaki Jerky is the stuff legends are made of. We’ve partnered with everyone’s favorite marinade company, Soy Vay, to combine their award winning Veri Veri Teriyaki Sauce with our tender Filet Mignon. Featuring salty, gingery and garlicky flavor notes, we’ve taken jerky from meh to mind blowing. We may be jerks, but their archetypical jerky is refined.
BEEF JERKY HONEY GLAZED Beef jerky made with high quality meat and real hardwood smoke. Sweetened with a honey glaze. Simply crafted with simple ingredients to be simply better.
BEEF JERKY OLD FASHIONED Beef Jerky Old Fashioned made with high-quality meat and real hardwood smoke. Seasoned to taste the same way it has from the start. Made in America using our family recipe.

BEEF JERKY SEA SALT & PEPPER Beef jerky made with high quality meat and real hardwood smoke. Seasoned with sea salt and fresh ground pepper. Simply crafted with simple ingredients to be simply better.
BEEF JERKY SPICY SWEET Beef Jerky Spicy Sweet made with high-quality meat and real hardwood smoke. Seasoned to taste the same way it has from the start. Made in America using our family recipe.

BEEF JERKY TERIYAKI Beef jerky made with high-quality meat and real hardwood smoke. Seasoned with our original recipe—using soy sauce and a touch of garlic. Simply crafted with simple ingredients to be simply better.
